This is a notification of your opportunity to terminate the discussion period and enter the decision making process early. If you all agree to do so by way of approval, the discussion phase will end and you're arbitrator will review all information and then make a decision.

In order to end early, the decision must be unanimous, meaning all parties must make the approval within 24 hours of this notification. If the request is rejected, you will be asked again the next day.

You may approve by going to the self service portal, or responding to this email.

